          <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrc="dd:2;115:15" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/indexterm.dita">Specifies that an index entry is positioned at the end of a range; value matches the
              <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:18;116:23" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/indexterm.dita">start</xmlatt> attribute on another <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:49;116:71" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/indexterm.dita">indexterm</xmlelement>.
